subject_information.comments: I didn't like not being warned that some of the answers were going to be filled in for me, instead of me writing all the directions as I'd been led to believe.  I also didn't like that when I ended sentences with a period it showed up instead as a set of three tildes.
subject_information.strategy: My strategy was to describe the color of the object, especially if I couldn't be as specific as I'd have liked to be with the terminology for the item itself.
